18. Be3{ White's idea behind  17.Rd3 , as now they are able to recapture with the rook on  e3 . }
18. Qxa4( { Starting with }18...Bxe3 { is fine as well and leads to the same thing after }19.Rxe3 Qxa4 20.Nxa4 { . } )
19. Nxa4
19. Bxe3
20. Rxe3
20. d4{ Forcing the trade of bishops and also making sure that  e2  is a target of counterplay, as White can no longer play  e2 - e3  easily. }
21. Rd3( { Black also has nothing to worry about in the event of }21.Bxb7 dxe3 22.Bxa8 exf2+ 23.Kxf2 Rxa8= { . } )
