8. Rc8{ Getting out of the long diagonal, so our rook will never be hanging, and also eyeing the  c4 -pawn. }
9. b4
9. Bd4
10. Ra2{ Our pieces are a bit loose here, but fortunately, we have a strong resource. }( { After }10.Nxd4?! Nxd4∓ { , White just loses a pawn, }{ as ... Rxc4  is coming next. } )
