10. Nc6( { Starting with }10...Nc7 { followed by ... Nc6  is fine as well. } )
11. O-O
11. Nc7
12. Nc3
12. Ne6( { White has compensation for the sacrificed pawn but for equality at most. This is not a line we should be worried about. }13.Nd5 { can be calmly met by }13...Qd8 { , }{ while finishing development with ... g6 , ... Bg7 , and ... O-O , or planting a knight on  d4  is something to look forward to. } )
