13. Qe8{ I recommend this move. It is also a novelty, so it could take our opponents by surprise. We will see the point behind this move later. }
14. Nh4{ This move is somewhat inaccurate, but it is still important to know what to do against it. }
14. d5{ Generally, it is nice to get this central pawn push in, to neutralize White's pressure. }
