5. Qa4{ This leads to a slower game and is generally chosen by players who want to avoid heavy theoretical battles. }
5. Bb7{ Now that we have lured out White's queen from  d1  to  a4 , we are going to prepare ... c5 , as White will not be able to meet that with  d5 . }
6. Bg2{ By far White's main move, continuing development. }
