10. a6( { Preparing to expand a bit on the queenside with ... b5 . Starting with }10...c5 { followed by ... a6  is also fine. } )
11. a4{ White can also restrict the ... b5  push, but Black is fine here as well. }
11. c5
12. Qe2
12. h6
13. Bf4
13. Ra7{ Followed by ... Qa8 . }
