16. Nd2{ The best retreating square for White's knight. White wants to reroute the knight now to  c4 , but fortunately, we can prevent that. }
16. Ne5{ Black has plenty of counterplay. Next, we are going to play ... Nh5  followed by either ... f5 , to try to break with ... f4 , or ... b5 , and after  axb6   Qxb6 , we will have a lot of play on the queenside. }
