10. h6{ The point behind this move is to play ... g5  quickly, forcing the bishop on  f4  to retreat so White will no longer have pressure on the  d6 -pawn. }
11. Qc1{ Attacking the pawn on  h6 , practically forcing us to play ... g5  right away. }
11. g5
