8. dxc5{ This is Le Quang Liem's suggestion in his London course. }( { If White still wants to place the knight on  e5 , they should do it now with }8.Ne5 { , as otherwise, we will prevent them from doing so with  8...Nbd7 . However, after }8...b6 { followed }{ by ... Ba6 , Black is doing absolutely fine. } )
